texts.desc:
Activate 1 of these effects for the rest of this turn;
 Once per turn, when an effect that would negate a Normal or Special Summon resolves, negate that effect.
 Once per turn, when an effect that would destroy a monster(s) resolves, negate that effect.

Activate 1 of these effects for the rest of this turn;
 Once per turn, when an effect that would negate the activation of a Spell Card resolves, negate that effect.
 Once per turn, when an effect that would destroy a Spell Card(s) resolves, negate that effect.

During damage calculation: Activate 1 of these effects;
 Monsters cannot be destroyed by this battle.
 Any battle damage from this battle becomes halved.

Once per turn: You can shuffle 1 card underneath this card into the Deck; inflict 1000 damage to your opponent. Once per turn, if this card has no cards underneath it: You can place 1 "Gladiator Beast" monster from your Deck underneath this card. Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can target 1 "Gladiator Beast" monster you control, then activate 1 of these effects;
 If the targeted monster battles: It cannot be destroyed by that battle, also you take no battle damage from that battle.
 If the targeted monster is targeted by a card effect: It cannot be destroyed by that effect.

Tribute 1 Link Monster, then target 1 "Borrel" Link Monster you control; equip this card to it, and if you do, place counters on this card equal to the Tributed Link Monster's Link Rating. The equipped monster is unaffected by your opponent's activated effects. Your opponent cannot target this equipped card with card effects. Once per battle, during damage calculation, if the equipped monster battles: You can remove 1 counter from this card, then activate 1 of these effects;
 Destroy the opponent's monster that battled the equipped monster after damage calculation, and if you do, inflict damage to your opponent equal to half the ATK that monster had on the field.
 Halve any battle damage you take from that battle.
